                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <title type="complete" ref="LIT4128Letter" xml:lang="gez"/> 
                    <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                    
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      መጽሐፈ፡ መልእክት፡ ዘንጉሠ፡ ነገሥተ፡ ዓለም፡ በተወልዶትነ፡ እምከርሠ፡ አሐቲ፡ እምነ፡ እንተ፡ ይእቲ፡ ጥምቀት፡
                      ዘተሰመይነ፡ ንሕነ፡ <persName ref="PRS5616IyasuI">ኢያሱ</persName>፤ ወበስመ፡ መንግሥትነ፡ 
                      ዘተሰመይነ፡ <persName ref="PRS5616IyasuI">አድያም፡ ሰገድ፡</persName> ገብረ፡ ንጉሠ፡ ነገሥተ፡ 
                      ዓለም፡ 
                      እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘይሤለስ፡ ወይትወሐድ። ወንጉሠ፡ ነገሥት፡ 
                      <persName ref="PRS5616IyasuI">አድያም፡ ሰገድ፡</persName> ወልደ፡ ንጉሠ፡ ነገሥተ፡ ዓለም፡
                      <persName ref="PRS10375Yohanne">አእላፍ፡ ሰገድ</persName>።  ወንጉሠ፡ ነገሥተ፡ ዓለም፡ 
                      <persName ref="PRS10375Yohanne">አእላፍ፡ ሰገድ፡</persName> ወልደ፡ ንጉሠ፡ 
                      <sic resp="DR">ንገሥተ፡</sic> ዓለም፡
                      <persName ref="PRS4015Fasilada">ዓለም፡ ሰገድ</persName>።
                      ወንጉሠ፡ ነገሥተ፡ ዓለም፡ <persName ref="PRS4015Fasilada">ዓለም፡ ሰገድ፡</persName> ወልደ፡ 
                      ንጉሠ፡ ነገሥተ፡ ዓለም፡ <persName ref="PRS9038Susenyos">ሥልጣን፡ ሰገድ</persName>።
                      ትብጻሕ፡ ኀበ፡ ብፁዕ፡
                      <persName ref="PRS3134Clement">ቀሌምንጦስ፡ ፓፓ፡ ሮሜ፡ አሠርቱ፡ ወአሐዱ</persName>። 
                      መጽሐፈ፡ መልእክትነሰ፡ ዘንጽሕፎ፡ ለከ። እስመ፡ ናሁ፡ ነገረነ፡ ዮሴፍ፡
                      ኵሎ፡ ዜና፡ ሀልዎትከ፡
                    </incipit>
                    
                    <note>Before the colophon <ref target="#coloph1"/>, there is a
                    signature of the king:
                      <q xml:lang="gez">ወአነ፡ <persName ref="PRS5616IyasuI">ኢያሱ፡</persName> ንጉሠ፡ <sic resp="PRS10747Zotenbe">ንገሥተ፡</sic> ኢትዮጵያ።</q></note>
                    
                    <colophon xml:id="coloph1" xml:lang="gez">
                      <date notBefore="1701" notAfter="1702" evidence="internal"/>
                      <note xml:lang="en">The letter was written in <placeName ref="gn:336014"/> in <date calendar="world"><foreign xml:lang="gez">Ṭǝrr</foreign> 7194, Era of the World</date>;
                        <date calendar="ethiopian">1694 Era of the 
                        Icarnation</date>; the 20th year of the reign of <persName ref="PRS5616IyasuI"/>. 
                        According to <persName ref="PRS10747Zotenbe"/>, the first two dates are wrong.</note>
                    </colophon>
                    
                    <note>An Arabic letter with the same content and origin is contained in BnF Arabe 321 <ref target="http://archivesetmanuscrits.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/cc89597m"/>.</note>
                    <note>A part from some omissions and transpositions, the text is nearly identitcal to <ref type="mss" corresp="BNFet162"/>.</note>
